{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_7_level_st_07-04","storyGroup":"main_7","storySort":20,"storyDependence":"main_7_level_st_07-03","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"7-20","storyName":"??:??:??","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"陈与塔露拉分别之夜，科西切与魏彦吾的对峙。\n以及，摄政王与赦罪师对他们计划的谈论。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_st_07-04","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"st_07-04","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":18,"characters":["科西切","魏彦吾","陈","塔露拉","？？？","赦罪师","摄政王"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"character","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_7_23.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"0.86","yScale":"0.86","fadetime":"0","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"5","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"我可以把她还给你，魏。","id":8},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"——","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"停！","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"......不要动手。","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"噢。你这些强大的刽子手，真是让我吃了很多苦头。","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"我当然可以把她还给你......但她身上的铐环会引爆龙门半数城区。","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"你......","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"魏，这是你曾经用来对付我的办法，是你逼我离开龙门的办法。","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"现在，我们主客易位。我是客人，也是下毒的人。","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"科西切。你害死了我的兄弟。","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"不，不，魏。是你自己杀了自己的兄弟。","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"我的角色并不重要。你兄弟的悲剧，也许出于一匹独角兽的密令，一条真龙的震怒，但泄露消息的究竟是不是我，不，不重要。","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"重要的是，魏，唯一重要的事实是——你用你手中的赤霄剑，杀了自己的兄弟。亲手。","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"赤霄，斩龙之剑。死在这剑下的是谁？血亲，义亲，至亲。","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"斩龙之剑？你们这些人铸造这把剑，不过用来同类相残。","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"你说得太多。","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"好。我让你选。","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"选吧。杀掉我抢回侄女，并因此毁掉这座城市；又或者允许我们平安离开。","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"——","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"不要出剑。你知道后果。","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"（牙齿研磨的声音）","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"放松些，魏。我已经允许你选了。如果你不选，那么我，你，你的市民，还有这一对惹人怜爱的姐妹，都会一起死。","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"你在盘算什么？","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"魏，魏......我了解你。我太了解你了。","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"你一直都有得选，不是吗？","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"你宝贵的市民们，一旦听说他们的生命被放在天平上，而另一边是一条没人知道姓名的幼龙，他们会怎么想？","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"而我甚至没有理由去伤害她。","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"......我既然疏忽到让你再踏上这座城市，就没理由再让你离开。","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"小塔！","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"真的吗？","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"......","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"我会亲手杀了你。","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"不必，不必。","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"我会死在正确的人手上。","id":41},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"image","id":44},{"type":"dialog","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_060","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"对了，在我给她戴上铐环前，你可以救下她的。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_060.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"可是你想着防范我，你想着战胜我，打倒我，毁灭我......想看我要做什么。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_060.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科西切","text":"魏，你其实害怕我，不是吗？","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_060.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"character","id":54},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":55},{"type":"background","id":56},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"她来了。","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"她终于来了。","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"亲手杀了她吧。","id":60},{"type":"character","id":61},{"type":"dialog","id":62},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"background","id":64},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":66,"musicid":1},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"赦罪师，回答。","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"整合运动的领袖，是否有结盟的价值？","id":68},{"type":"dialog","id":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_055","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"你很清楚的事情又何必问我，摄政王殿下？","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"一个没有积累、没有背景、没有资本的青年，不可能凭一己之力拿下乌萨斯的重要城市。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"身为非感染者的统治者们，并不清楚蕴含在她行为里的逻辑。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"他们会一味恐惧，反应过激，尝试通过破坏性的行为去解决混乱的局面——感染者带来的混乱局面。","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"但我们萨卡兹再清楚不过了。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"character","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_062","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摄政王","text":"至于她留在这里的队伍，你的看法是？","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_062.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_055","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"没有前景，殿下，正如你预见的那样，并没有什么前景。他们并不是真正的军队，而我们需要的是足够的暴力。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_062","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摄政王","text":"剪除他们不能削弱塔露拉的力量。我们缺少一个消灭她的机会。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_062.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_055","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"是的，殿下。","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"她所带来的局面、她搅动局面所需要的力量，都恰恰说明她并不是一个单纯的感染者领袖，或是做好了准备去继承皇冠的王储。","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"她是个阴谋家。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_062","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摄政王","text":"即使如此，我也需要萨卡兹的全面响应。","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_062.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_055","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"那么，我有两个好消息，第一是，对于“魔王”的搜查，已经有眉目了。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"罗德岛从未易手过。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_062","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摄政王","text":"来不及。我们必须立刻让她开始。","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_062.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_055","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"请不要发怒，允许我说出第二个吧。","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赦罪师","text":"“她”已经准备好了。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_055.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":100},{"type":"character","id":101},{"type":"background","id":102},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_avg_7_21.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"0.86","yScale":"0.86","fadetime":"0","id":104},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_7_22.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"0.86","yScale":"0.86","fadetime":"0","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摄政王","text":"这才是我们应有的力量。","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摄政王","text":"萨卡兹的正统王者，比任何不知名姓的继承人都强。","id":112},{"type":"character","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"image","id":116}],"characters":["科西切","魏彦吾","陈","塔露拉","？？？","赦罪师","摄政王"]}